  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO BE KNOWN AS THE \"GOLD AND SILVER COMMEMORATIVE COIN ACT\"; TO AUTHORIZE THE STATE TREASURER TO ENTER INTO A CONTRACTUAL AGREEMENT WITH A PUBLIC OR PRIVATE MINTING COMPANY FOR THE PURPOSES OF MINTING ONE-OUNCE GOLD STATE COMMEMORATIVE COINS OR ONE-OUNCE SILVER COMMEMORATIVE COINS FOR THE STATE OF MISSISSIPPI; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
